Get ready to look your perfect self ALL. SUMMER. LONG with Facelab! Retouch your ‘flawsome’ selfies & portraits with a go-to set of essential tools & filters. In an instant!

Here what’s new:

• No drooping mouth corners! Get up-turned lips with an all-new lip lift ‘Smile’ tool! Best paired with those pearly bright whites.
• Buzz, buzz, buzz! The vibrations on successful and failed actions added.
• Routine bug fixes and performance improvements.

Treat yo’self right,
~ Facelab Team

Easy, Fun, AI-Powered Selfie Beautifier! Retouch your 'flawsome' selfies & portraits with a go-to set of essential tools & pro filters. In an instant!

- All-new Retouch section with 10 powerful tools for every selfie you take. Going wrong with a selection? Just use the Eraser!
- Remove the unwanted shine in just a few taps with 'Matte' tool!
- Highlight & add an extra boost of glow to your portrait with 'Glow' tool!
- Enhance your eyes and add that fresh-look energy to your gaze with the 'Sharpen' tool.
- 'Skin Patch' and 'Reshape' tools get upgraded! Nothing gets missed! Now with manual zoom for even more precise & easier editing, and moving areas as needed!
- B&W your photo with any object jumping out with color!
- Less bugs, tons of under-the-hood improvements.

Much Love,
~ Facelab Team
